Package com.catenax.tdm.scenario

Class TestDataScenarioBaseListener

java.lang.Object
com.catenax.tdm.scenario.TestDataScenarioBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
TestDataScenarioListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
Direct Known Subclasses:
TestDataScenarioExecutor
public class TestDataScenarioBaseListener
extends Object
implements TestDataScenarioListener
This class provides an empty implementation of TestDataScenarioListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
